    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines a portion of the Management Information Base (MIB) module for use with network management protocols in the Internet community.  In particular, it describes a set of managed objects that are used to manage Telephony Routing over IP (TRIP) devices. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
